@startuml t_sequence_07_skinparam_title_misc
title Sequence Diagram — Skinparam, Title, Header, Footer,\nComments, hide footbox, pragma teoz

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 1. MULTI-LINE TITLE (title...end title block form)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

' Note: title keyword above uses single-line form.
' The block form is:
'   title
'   line one
'   line two
'   end title
' (tested in comment form here; single-line used above)

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 2. HEADER and FOOTER
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

header
    **Document Header**
    System: OT Edge AI Platform
    Version: 2.4.1
    Classification: CONFIDENTIAL
end header

footer
    Page %page% of %lastpage%
    Generated: 2026-03-31
    © Pictosync Systems
end footer

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 3. SKINPARAM — all sequence-relevant forms
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderThickness 1.2
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderThickness 1.0
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #666666

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #444444
    ArrowFontSize 10
    ArrowFontColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderColor #888888
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #EEEEEE
    ParticipantBorderColor #2C7BB6
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
    ParticipantFontSize 12
    ParticipantFontColor #000000
    ActorBorderColor #E65100
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
    ActorFontSize 12
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BoxBorderColor #CCCCCC
    GroupBorderColor #555555
    GroupBackgroundColor #F0F0F0
    GroupFontSize 11
    GroupFontColor #333333
    GroupHeaderFontSize 12
    DividerBackgroundColor #E0E0E0
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    DividerFontColor #444444
    DividerFontSize 11
    NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
    NoteBorderColor #F9A825
    NoteFontColor #4E342E
    NoteFontSize 10
    ReferenceBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
    ReferenceBorderColor #2E7D32
    ReferenceFontSize 10
}

skinparam participant {
    Padding 5
    BorderThickness 1.2
}

skinparam actor {
    BorderThickness 1.0
}

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 4. HIDE FOOTBOX
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

hide footbox

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 5. PRAGMA TEOZ — enables multiline arrow anchoring
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

!pragma teoz true

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 6. PARTICIPANTS (styled by skinparam above)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

actor     "Grid Operator"     as OP
boundary  "API Gateway"       as GW
control   "Auth Controller"   as AC
entity    "Order Entity"      as OE
database  "TimescaleDB"       as DB
queue     "NATS Queue"        as NQ
participant "Edge AI Node"    as AI

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 7. SINGLE-LINE COMMENTS  '
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

' This is a single-line comment — ignored by parser
' Comments can appear anywhere between statements
' Multiple consecutive comments are valid

OP -> GW : login request
' comment between messages
GW -> AC : authenticate
' another comment
AC --> GW : token
' final comment before response
GW --> OP : session token

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 8. MULTI-LINE COMMENTS  /' ... '/
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

/' 
    This is a multi-line comment block.
    It can span multiple lines.
    It is completely ignored by the parser.
    Useful for temporarily disabling sections.
    
    participant "Disabled" as DIS
    DIS -> GW : this message is commented out
'/

OP -> GW : data request

/'
    Another multi-line comment.
    GW -> DB : this is hidden
    DB --> GW : hidden response
'/

GW -> DB : actual data query
DB --> GW : data

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 9. TEOZ PRAGMA — multiline arrow (concurrent arrows)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== teoz concurrent arrows ==

OP -> GW : startConcurrentOp() {start}
GW -> AC : validateAsync()
AC --> GW : valid
GW -> NQ : enqueueJob() {end}
GW --> OP : jobQueued

NQ -> AI : processJob()
activate AI
AI -> DB : storeResult()
activate DB
DB --> AI : stored
deactivate DB
AI --> NQ : jobComplete
deactivate AI

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 10. FULL DIAGRAM EXERCISE — all features together
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== full integration ==

autonumber 1 1 "<b>(%d)</b>"

OP -> GW : submitOrder(payload)
activate GW #FFE0B2

note right of OP : operator initiates order

alt payload valid
    GW -> AC : authorize(token)
    activate AC #E3F2FD

    opt token cached
        AC -> DB : checkTokenCache()
        activate DB #E8F5E9
        DB --> AC : cached token data
        deactivate DB
    end

    AC --> GW : authorized
    deactivate AC

    GW -> OE : createOrder(payload)
    activate OE #FCE4EC

    loop up to 3 retries
        OE -> DB : persistOrder()
        activate DB
        
        break on DB error
            OE --> GW : persistence failed
        end
        
        DB --> OE : orderId=42
        deactivate DB
    end

    OE -> NQ : publishOrderEvent()
    activate NQ
    NQ --> OE : published
    deactivate NQ

    par async notifications
        NQ -> AI : analyzeOrder()
        activate AI
        AI -> DB : storeAnalysis()
        activate DB
        DB --> AI : stored
        deactivate DB
        AI --> NQ : analysis complete
        deactivate AI
    else async logging
        NQ -> DB : logEvent()
        activate DB
        DB --> NQ : logged
        deactivate DB
    end

    OE --> GW : order 42 created
    deactivate OE

    GW --> OP : 201 Created\norderId=42
    deactivate GW

else payload invalid
    GW --> OP : 400 Bad Request
    deactivate GW
end

autonumber stop

... processing async events ...

|||

== async completion ==

NQ -> OP : orderConfirmed(42)

note over OP, GW
    Order lifecycle complete.
    All async events processed.
end note

== end of document ==

note right of AI
    **Grammar targets (misc):**
    title (single + multi-line)
    header / end header
    footer / end footer
    skinparam key value
    skinparam key { block }
    skinparam type<<stereo>> { }
    hide footbox
    show footbox
    !pragma teoz true
    ' single-line comment
    /' multi-line comment '/
    autonumber formats
    Concurrent teoz arrows {start}{end}
end note

@enduml
